Classes.Description: Synchronized steps, country beats, and zero need for a dance partner. No boots please.

Come experience group fitness with this indoor cycling class - an energetic, music-driven spin class that fuels your body and fires up your mood. Great for beginners to advanced individuals because YOU control your pace and resistance.
Move and have fun in the water to a variety of upbeat music for an invigorating workout. All fitness levels are welcome.
